 solid foundation in algorithms and data structures, I apply analytical thinking to build efficient and scalable applications. My exposure to data science principles enables me to work with data strategically, extracting insights that support intelligent decision-making.\r\n\r\nMy interests extend to full-stack and backend development, where I work on building structured, maintainable systems designed for long-term efficiency and growth.", "profile_image": "profile_images/profile_2rUSn3r.jpg", "skills": "", "github_url": "https://github.com/suprit2005", "linkedin_url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/suprit-mahajan-520077298/", "email_contact": "supritmahajan@gmail.com", "role": "Aspiring Software Developer, Data & Analytics Enthusiast", "resume": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hDso4viKFg-9SIwxLuRdETYCun1EsUs5/view?usp=sharing"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 3, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Bachelor of Technology - Computer Science Engineering", "institution_name": "Lovely Professional University", "start_date": "2023-08-15", "end_date": null, "is_current": true, "location": "Phagwara, Punjab"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 7, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Matriculation", "institution_name": "Maharishi Vidya Mandir", "start_date": "2019-04-18", "end_date": "2021-03-20", "is_current": false, "location": "Fatehpur, U.P."}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 8, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Intermediate", "institution_name": "Maharishi Vidya Mandir", "start_date": "2021-04-22", "end_date": "2023-03-20", "is_current": false, "location": "Fatehpur, U.P."}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Air Quality Health Risk Analysis", "slug": "air-quality-health-riskanalysis", "summary": "Machine learning-based system that predicts health risk levels using air pollution indicators. Built with multiple supervised models and deployed through an interactive Streamlit dashboard.", "description": "Built an end-to-end ML solution to classify health risk levels using pollution data (PM2.5, PM10, NO₂, CO, SO₂, O₃).\r\nApplied preprocessing and trained multiple supervised learning models; achieved 98.91% accuracy.\r\nCreated evaluation visuals and deployed the model using Streamlit for real-time predictions.", "tech_stack": "Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Machine Learning", "github_link": "https://github.com/suprit2005/Air-Quality-Health-Risk-Analysis", "live_demo_link": null, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2025-12-07_231450.png", "featured": false, "created_date": "2026-02-24T04:15:40.472Z"}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "Seattle Airbnb Data Analysis & Price Prediction", "slug": "seattle-airbnb-data-analysis-price-prediction", "summary": "A structured data science project analyzing Seattle Airbnb listings through SQL preprocessing, Python-based EDA, interactive Power BI dashboards, and predictive modeling to understand pricing and demand trends.", "description": "Cleaned and preprocessed Seattle Airbnb dataset using SQL by handling missing values, duplicates.\r\nPerformed EDA using Python to analyze pricing trends, listing patterns; built a Power BI dashboard.\r\nDeveloped ML models to predict prices and evaluated performance using RMSE and R².", "tech_stack": "SQL, Python, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Scikit-learn, Power BI", "github_link": "https://github.com/suprit2005/Seattle-Airbnb-Data-Science-Project", "live_demo_link": null, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2026-02-24_100343.png", "featured": false, "created_date": "2026-02-24T04:35:57.238Z"}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 9, "fields": {"title": "Career Connect – Job Portal", "slug": "career-connect-job-portal", "summary": "abc", "description": "Developed a Django-based job portal with user registration, login, and job application features.\r\nImplemented job posting, listing, and application management with database integration.\r\nD